All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AbstractServiceSql
Abstract base class for ServiceSql implementations that validates SQL queries by executing them.
DatabaseStringGenerator
Generates a database-specific string representation for a given set of JPA entity types.
DatabaseStringGeneratorImpl
Utility class for analyzing the JPA metamodel and the underlying database schema.
DomainStringGenerator
Generates a domain-specific string representation for a given set of JPA entity types.
DomainStringGeneratorImpl
Utility class for generating domain-specific string representations of JPA entity types.
EntityTypeSelection
Data structure for managing the selection state of JPA entity types and related configuration.
JpaAccess
Central access point for JPA-related resources within the library.
JpaAccessHolder
Internal singleton holder for the JpaAccess instance.
ServiceSql
Service interface for SQL dialect information and query validation.
ServiceSqlImpl
Concrete implementation of AbstractServiceSql that validates and executes SQL queries using the application's configured JPA and Hibernate infrastructure.
SimpleEntityTypeSelection
Simple data structure for managing the selection state of a set of JPA entity types, along with configuration for prompt generation and string representation.
UMLGenerator
Generates a UML diagram as an image stream for a given set of JPA entity types.
UMLGeneratorImpl
Utility class for generating UML diagram images from a set of JPA entity types.
